stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Healthy
    Healthy --> Unhealthy: Repeated probe failures
    note right of Healthy
      Included in routing pool
      Receives normal traffic
    end note

    Unhealthy --> Recovering: Probe returns 200-299 again
    Unhealthy --> Replaced: Remains unhealthy for long period
    note right of Unhealthy
      Removed from load balancer pool
      New requests stop flowing here
    end note

    Recovering --> Healthy: Consecutive successful probes
    Recovering --> Unhealthy: Probe fails again
    note right of Recovering
      Gradual trust restored
      Eligible to receive traffic again
    end note

    Replaced --> [*]
